Metadata.Title: Bodyguards Vs Assassin Pt. 2
Metadata.Description: Ugh, 47, these bozos are still up and running despite us killing all their clients. Can't they take a hint?! I say we try to be a bit louder with our next attack. A big and important fashonshow has hired a ton of bodyguards to keep everything in order. Do away with these clowns in your superior suit and we'll be seen as heros in the ICA!
